title: Last of the Comanches (1953 - USA) [multi subs] western
description:
Last of the Comanches (1953 - USA)                   aka The Sabre and the Arrow

Action / Adventure / Western

starring . . . . Broderick Crawford, Barbara Hale, Johnny Stewart, Lloyd Bridges
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0044828/


Filmed at Arizona, USA [Yuma, Tucson, Mojave Desert, Sierrita Mountains]

With Sgt. Matt Trainor as its Leading Commander, what's left of a massacred cavalry troop from the isolated frontier town of Dry Buttes, along with a ragtag group of stagecoach passengers, fight for survival at a desert ruin against fierce Comanches led by Black Cloud.

This movie is a remake of the 1943 World War II film Sahara, starring Humphrey Bogart. Actor Lloyd Bridges appeared in both films.
